<p>
<note n="0399005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0399005">第五十七＝第八十一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0400001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0400001">二＋（智）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0400002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0400002">若＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0400003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0400003">墮＝惰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0401002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0401002">〔以〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0401003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0401003">心＋（心）【宋】【元】【明】</note>
